		<title>Germany is NSA&#039;s largest listening post, according to new report based on Snowden&#160;leaks</title>
		<link>http://boingboing.net/2014/06/18/germany-is-nsas-largest-list.html</link>
		<comments>http://boingboing.net/2014/06/18/germany-is-nsas-largest-list.html#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Wed, 18 Jun 2014 19:42:28 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Xeni Jardin]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Post]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[edward snowden]]></category>
