		<title>Crowdfunding for Cryptome, oldest radical secrets-leaking site&#160;online</title>
		<link>http://boingboing.net/2014/05/29/crowdfunding-for-cryptome-old.html</link>
		<comments>http://boingboing.net/2014/05/29/crowdfunding-for-cryptome-old.html#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Thu, 29 May 2014 19:50:29 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Xeni Jardin]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Post]]></category>
