		<description><![CDATA[<p>I&#39;m fine. Heathrow&#39;s Border Force was just trying to intimidate me. &#34;Who is Edward Snowden?&#34; &#34;Do you know him?&#34; &#34;Where is Bradley Manning?&#34;</p>&#8212; Jesselyn Radack (@JesselynRadack) <a href="https://twitter.com/JesselynRadack/statuses/435026335812300800">February 16, 2014</a>


