		<title>US drones could be killing the wrong people because of metadata&#160;errors</title>
		<link>http://boingboing.net/2014/02/10/us-drones-could-be-killing-the.html</link>
		<comments>http://boingboing.net/2014/02/10/us-drones-could-be-killing-the.html#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2014 18:04:44 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Xeni Jardin]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Post]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[DRONES]]></category>
